1. Create a game board
    create a 3*3 array to gather the inputs
2. Total 8 win conditions
        - all elements in a row are same(3)
        - all elements in a col are same(3)
        - all elements in a diagonal are same(2)
3. Check win or tie conditions

Optional:
    - take input from end user
            or
    - use random way to get the empty position
